title: Truth Phoenix (One) Pdf
description:
Truth Phoenix (One) Pdf
-----------------------

This book is a collection of poems and reflections written over a period of 14 years (2005 - 2018) by a Vancouver writer.

These two Pdf files contain the same book.

- The Digital Edition is for those who prefer to read on monitors, laptops, tablets, or phones.

- The Print Edition is for those who prefer to read hard copy. It has been arranged to enable double-sided printing into a booklet.

Peace, love, and transparency... E:)
